data.description: Welcome To Your New Home at Whitewater Estates. A communal equestrian arena and 6 miles of equestrian/public trail access and a 2.375% assumable VA loan are waiting for you. This incredibly maintained and gorgeous 3 bed 2.5 bath Rambler comes complete with a beautifully manicured fenced in garden complete with very own garden shed, 3 car attached garage, with generator transfer, and a 1200 sq ft detached 2 car pull through garage with RV/Boat parking and workshop space. The interior is light and airy, hosts tall ceilings and hardwood floors in kitchen and eating area. Updated cabinets and appliances fill the kitchen. Relax and keep cozy by the wood burning fire stove in the living room. Don't miss out! These homes do not come around often.
